93.title: Adiós 20añero
93.plot: Jano learned of a painful truth that for years his mother hid him, which helped him partly explain his envy towards Pancho and forced him to give a last blow. What did he do to the twenty-year-old?

imdb.plot outline: After being in a coma for 27 years Pancho Bustamante wakes up in a different body and a world he doesn't remember. Fascinated by the political, social and technological changes that happened during this time he's also disappointed because the future is not exactly what he expected.
imdb.title: 20añero a los 40
plot: At the age of 20 a young man suffers an accident and remains in a coma, 20 years later awakens in a time when everything is different and in the body of a man of 40 years old but with a mentality of a twenty-something.

After being in a coma for 27 years Pancho Bustamante wakes up in a different body and a world he doesn't remember. Fascinated by the political, social and technological changes that happened during this time he's also disappointed because the future is not exactly what he expected.
